claim.claim-text:
1. An assembly fixture for assembling a hinge to a display panel assembly, comprising:
a base for supporting the display panel assembly; and
at least one hinge mounting member fixed on the base, and each said mounting member comprising:
two support bars protruding from the base;
an axle rotatably connected to the two support bars;
a rotatable arm fixed to the axle, said rotatable arm comprising at least two protruding portions for positioning a connecting portion of the hinge, and at least one magnetic element for fixing the connecting portion of the hinge to the rotatable arm.
